{"type": "article", "id": 3929, "title": "HUSH 隔音耳塞", "description": "", "date": "2014-11-28T07:55:05Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 8, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233133Mp1h9GqvmSWYlXo5.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t睡眠很浅？房间隔音效果太差？你可能需要一款隔音耳塞。这玩意儿现在市面上已经很多，但是一款帮助你不漏掉任何重要信息、不会睡过头的耳塞，相信你一定会感兴趣。来自加州圣地亚哥的创业团队 HUSH 日前就带来了这样一款产品，能够在帮你隔绝外界噪音的同时，它还具有播放功能，预设的轻音乐可以帮助你快速入眠。当然，你还需要下载一款相应的 App 产品，然后设置闹钟、重要联系人的来电与消息提醒，就不会漏掉重要信息了。目前，这款耳塞正在<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/hush/hush-the-worlds-first-smart-earplug\" target=\"_blank\"> Kickstarter </a>上众筹，起售价 99 美元，预计明年 5 月出货。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233131qhm1ijFR8g6btSkJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233131DFIOUwNEP8sf6Azb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233132WKd0yePNLZMs6mJE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233132j6gABkaYt8bZFOC0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/ksr/assets/002/888/524/5a50ebd98064c6d4358e87a04a3a1586_large.gif?1415672952\" width=\"640\" alt=\"\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}